#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.73"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.73:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.73:0.2"
msgid "7. Migajālavagga"
msgstr "7. With Migajāla"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn35.73:0.3"
msgid "73. Tatiyachaphassāyatanasutta"
msgstr "73. Six Fields of Contact (3rd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.45"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca "
"atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, anyone who doesn’t truly understand the six fields of contact’s "
"origin, ending, gratification, drawback, and escape"

msgctxt "sn35.73:1.2"
msgid "Avusitaṃ tena brahmacariyaṃ, ārakā so imasmā dhammavinayā”ti."
msgstr ""
"has not completed the spiritual journey and is far from this teaching and "
"training.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, aññataro bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, one of the mendicants said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn35.73:2.2"
msgid "“etthāhaṃ, bhante, anassasaṃ panassasaṃ."
msgstr "“Here, sir, I’m lost, truly lost."

msgctxt "sn35.73:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ahañhi, bhante, channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca "
"ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"For I don’t truly understand the six fields of contact’s origin, ending, "
"gratification, drawback, and escape.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:3.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, bhikkhu, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicant? "

msgctxt "sn35.73:3.2"
msgid "cakkhu niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "Is the eye permanent or impermanent?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:4.1"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:5.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:6.1"
msgid "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Suffering, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:7.1"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhammaṃ, kallaṃ nu taṃ samanupassituṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“But if it’s impermanent, suffering, and liable to fall apart, is it fit to "
"be regarded thus:"

msgctxt "sn35.73:7.2"
msgid "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’”ti?"
msgstr "‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:8.1"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“No, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:9.1"
msgid "“Sotaṃ …"
msgstr "“Is the ear …"

msgctxt "sn35.73:9.2"
msgid "ghānaṃ …"
msgstr "nose …"

msgctxt "sn35.73:9.3"
msgid "jivhā …"
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "sn35.73:9.4"
msgid "kāyo …"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "sn35.73:9.5"
msgid "mano nicco vā anicco vā”ti?"
msgstr "mind permanent or impermanent?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:10.1"
msgid "“Anicco, bhante”."
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:11.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:12.1"
msgid "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Suffering, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:13.1"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhammaṃ, kallaṃ nu taṃ samanupassituṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“But if it’s impermanent, suffering, and liable to fall apart, is it fit to "
"be regarded thus:"

msgctxt "sn35.73:13.2"
msgid "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’”ti?"
msgstr "‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:14.1"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“No, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:15.1"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhu, sutavā ariyasāvako cakkhusmimpi nibbindati, "
"sotasmimpi nibbindati, ghānasmimpi nibbindati, jivhāyapi nibbindati, "
"kāyasmimpi nibbindati, manasmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"“Seeing this, a learned noble disciple becomes disillusioned with the eye, "
"ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind."

msgctxt "sn35.73:15.2"
msgid ""
"Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati; vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned they become dispassionate. Being dispassionate they’re "
"freed. When freed, they know ‘it is freed’."

msgctxt "sn35.73:15.3"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānātī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.73:15.4"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.73:15.5"
msgid "Migajālavaggo dutiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.73:16.1"
msgid "Migajālena dve vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.73:16.2"
msgid "Cattāro ca samiddhinā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.73:16.3"
msgid "Upaseno upavāṇo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.73:16.4"
msgid "Chaphassāyatanikā tayoti."
msgstr ""
